name: 6  Tribal Shields - Tau Tribe
description:
Tau ~ (Tribe of The Lion) 

Manes of Gold. Fierce strength. Masters of the hierarchy. Kings and Queens in waiting. This is the embodiment of this Tribe.
Ancient and wise with an ingrained ability to defend and protect. The still water of their Hearts runs exceedingly deep and their resolve is impenetrable. The Pride is filled with Leaders. There is no straying from the pack. The elders to the youngest are prepared for battle yet none will provoke and this is the way it shall always be.
Warriors of Faith and Ferocity.
